dct_title_s: Sketch map of the route of the R.G.S. East African expedition from Dar es Salaam to Lake Nyassa, 1879
dct_description_sm: Route of expedition shown in red. Previous routes of Stanley, Burton, Speke, Cameron, Elton, and Von der Decken also shown. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 2 (1880), no. 2, pp. 102-22; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
